{"tid":2393251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（爭奪人心）「兩岸政治人物民望」排行榜　習近平排第6  低過李克強","createTime":"2021-02-03T10:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T11:50:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"98dc527a158c35bd86dd5ce4d6d68589dd2a53dd","tid":2393251,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T10:31:46.000Z","msg":"據香港民意機構發布的最新兩岸領導人民望排行，名列前3的都是已卸任的前中國領導人，總統蔡英文排名第5，中國國家主席習近平排名第6。香港學者呼籲北京當局應思考這個排名反映的意義。<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所2日公布2021年上半年「兩岸政治人物民望評分」，結果顯示，在10位香港市民最熟悉的中國及台灣領導人之中，前中國國務院總理朱鎔基名列第1，分數為67.7分；前中國總理溫家寶排名第2，得分為61.9分；緊接其後的是前中共總書記胡錦濤，得分58分。<br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平在排名中名列第6，低於總統蔡英文與中國國務院總理李克強。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=892676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D892676&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=df5b4a8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D892676&h=e92f5652\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=892676</a>"},{"pid":"0ed9af6fdb580ec0435c097d4f86aa18a15da3f5","tid":2393251,"uid":313692,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T10:34:34.000Z","msg":"李克強RAP<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da1919698a7f33f3b115b640d237b51da0f40f1","tid":2393251,"uid":184679,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T10:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://memeprod.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com/meme/74c78e7bf416e8ddd622ce8ebc5dd7d2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmemeprod.sgp1.digitaloceanspaces.com%2Fmeme%2F74c78e7bf416e8ddd622ce8ebc5dd7d2.png&h=b04502f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41f9cbbd53395627bf525248727c57ea5c69b776","tid":2393251,"uid":382962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T10:44:04.000Z","m